text: The good news for Coe is that he has gotten engaged again. He said he popped the question about a month ago and plans to marry next year. He said he doesn't plan to publicly reveal his fiancee's name just yet because he doesn't "want to jinx that with all the media attention," but he is willing to have Washington officiate the wedding for real.
title: 'Gary from Chicago' has experienced ups and downs since his Oscars cameo
